    <item>
      <title>伦敦被忽视的外围行政区帮助推动创纪录的租金上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/london-s-overlooked-outer-boroughs-help-drive-record-rent-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦长期被忽视的外围行政区帮助将首都的租金通胀率推升至有记录以来的最高水平，加剧了租户的生活成本危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/london-s-overlooked-outer-boroughs-help-drive-record-rent-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米其林挑战欧盟寻找轮胎卡特尔证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着监管机构席卷整个轮胎行业，寻找涉嫌垄断价格卡特尔的证据，米其林正在挑战欧盟对其设施进行反垄断搜查的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/michelin-challenges-eu-s-hunt-for-evidence-of-tire-cartel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据日经新闻报道，东芝将在最新重组计划中裁员 5,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/toshiba-to-cut-5-000-jobs-in-latest-bid-to-restructure-nikkei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《日经新闻》报道，东芝公司正寻求在日本裁员 5,000 人，约占其员工总数的 10%，这凸显了日本长期劳动力短缺的情况下，裁员的耻辱正在逐渐消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/toshiba-to-cut-5-000-jobs-in-latest-bid-to-restructure-nikkei</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
